movie.title: The Final Countdown
movie.plot: During routine manoeuvres near Hawaii in 1980, the aircraft-carrier USS Nimitz is caught in a strange vortex-like storm, throwing the ship back in time to 1941â€”mere hours before the Japanese attack on Pearl Harbor.
